extends ./template.pug

block tabs
	li
		a(href="/") Faucet
	li
		a(href="/cooldowns") Cooldowns
	li.is-active
		a(href="/about") About

block body
	article.tile.notification.is-info.is-child
		p.title.has-text-centered.is-family-monospace XNUFaucet v#{locals.versionString}

		p.subtitle.has-text-centered Developed by 
			code TheDevMinerTV#9308
			|  for Xenium.

		p Written on the 30th of November 2019 in one day as a successor to the never released 
			code XNUFaucet
			|  written by me and Waterdev.

		p Special thanks to 
			li
				a(href="https://github.com/UnrealValentin") Waterdev | Valentin

		br

		p Communication to the wallet using 
			a(href="https://github.com/turtlecoin/turtlecoin-rpc-js") Turtlecoin-RPC,
			|  routing using 
			a(href="") Express,
			|  rendering using 
			a(href="") Pug
			|  and as the database we are using 
			a(href="") NeDB
			| .

		p For the frontend, we are using 
			a(href="https://bulma.io") Bulma
			|  for CSS/styling.
